and numbered them, in order to personally arrange them in expositions and when on display.<ref name=\"Artmapp Fr\u00fchjahr 2017\" />\n\n<gallery widths=\"132\" heights=\"180\" perrow=\"6\">\nEgon Tschirch- Hohelied Nr. 1 (high resolution).jpg|'''''No. 1'''''\nEgon Tschirch- Hohelied Nr. 2 (high resolution).jpg|'''''No. 2'''''\nEgon Tschirch- Hohelied Nr. 3 (high resolution).jpg|'''''No. 3'''''\nEgon Tschirch- Hohelied Nr. 4 (high resolution).jpg|'''''No. 4'''''\nEgon Tschirch- Hohelied Nr. 5 (high resolution).jpg|'''''No. 5''''' \nEgon Tschirch- Hohelied Nr. 6 (high resolution).jpg|'''''No. 6''''' \nEgon Tschirch- Hohelied Nr. 7 (high resolution).jpg|'''''No. 7''''' \nEgon Tschirch- Hohelied Nr. 8 (high resolution).jpg|'''''No. 8''''' \nEgon Tschirch- Hohelied Nr. 9 (high resolution).jpg|'''''No. 9''''' \nEgon Tschirch- Hohelied Nr. 10 (high resolution).jpg|'''''No. 10''''' \nEgon Tschirch- Hohelied Nr. 12 (high resolution).jpg|'''''No. 12''''' \nEgon Tschirch- Hohelied Nr. 13 (high resolution).jpg|'''''No. 13''''' \nEgon Tschirch- Hohelied Nr. 14 (high resolution).jpg|'''''No. 14''''' \nEgon Tschirch- Hohelied Nr. 15 (high resolution).jpg|'''''No. 15''''' \nEgon Tschirch- Hohelied Nr. 16 (high resolution).jpg|'''''No. 16''''' \nEgon Tschirch- Hohelied Nr. 17 (high resolution).jpg|'''''No. 17''''' \nEgon Tschirch- Hohelied Nr. 18 (high resolution).jpg|'''''No. 18''''' \nEgon Tschirch- Hohelied Nr. 19 (high resolution).jpg|'''''No. 19''''' \n</gallery>\n\n== Background ==\nSince 1913 Egon Tschirch had been working (with war-time interruptions) on the topic of the Song of Solomon.  On Easter Sunday 1923, his special exhibit opened in the [[Abbey of the Holy Cross, Rostock|city museum of Rostock]].<ref name=\"Rostocker Anzeiger\">''Rostocker Anzeiger'', April 4, 1923</ref> It met with critical acclaim and thus in 1924 the [[Staatliches Museum Schwerin|state museum in Schwerin]] also showed this cycle of paintings.<ref name=\"Nachrichten Schwerin\">''Mecklenburger Nach