ory:Data unit]]\n[[Category:Units of information]]\n\n\n{{compu-stub}}\n", "name_user": "ShootSniper", "label": "safe", "comment": "fix a wrong word segmentation.", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Syllable_(computing)"}
